'''1,3,5-三硫雜環己烷'''是一種[[有機硫化合物|含硫]]六元[[雜環化合物|雜環化合物]]，化學式為{{chem|(CH|2|S)|3}}。此分子為[[硫代甲醛|硫代甲醛]]的[[三聚體|三聚體]]，以甲基化架橋分別連接三個硫醚結構而成。

== 性質 ==
[[File:SymTrithiane.jpg|thumb]]
1,3,5-三硫雜環己烷可在酸性環境中以[[硫化氫|硫化氫]]與[[甲醛|甲醛]]的反應製備而成。<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.15227/orgsyn.016.0081|url=http://orgsyn.org/Content/pdfs/procedures/CV2P0610.pdf|last1=Bost|first1=R. W.|last2=Constable|first2=E. W.|title=sym-Trithiane|journal=Organic Syntheses|volume=16|pp=81|year=1936|access-date=2020-08-02|archive-date=2017-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170918155512/http://orgsyn.org/Content/pdfs/procedures/CV2P0610.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

:3 HCHO + 3 H<sub>2</sub>S →  C<sub>3</sub>H<sub>6</sub>S<sub>3</sub> + 3 H<sub>2</sub>O

此化合物可作為[[有機合成|有機合成]]的建構組元，用於甲醯基化合物的製備。一個例子是[[有機鋰試劑|有機鋰試劑]]將三硫雜環己烷[[去質子化|去質子]]後成為鋰衍生物，其後再對其進行[[烷基化|烷基化]]（而除了三硫雜環己烷外其他[[縮硫醛|雙縮硫醛]]也可進行類似反應）：<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.15227/orgsyn.051.0039|last1=Seebach|first1=D.|last2=Beck|first2=A. K.|title=Aldehydes From ''sym''-Ttrithiane: ''n''-Pentadecanal|journal=Organic Syntheses|volume=51|pp=39|year=1971|url=http://orgsyn.org/Content/pdfs/procedures/CV6P0869.pdf|access-date=2020-08-02|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304110749/http://orgsyn.org/Content/pdfs/procedures/CV6P0869.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

:(CH{{sub|2}}S){{sub|3}} + RLi → (CH{{sub|2}}S){{sub|2}}(CHLiS) + RH
:(CH{{sub|2}}S){{sub|2}}(CHLiS) + R'Br → (CH{{sub|2}}S){{sub|2}}(CHR'S) + LiBr
:(CH{{sub|2}}S){{sub|2}}(CHR'S) + H{{sub|2}}O → R'CHO + …

此化合物也可備出其他有機硫試劑，如在水中進行氯化可形成氯甲基硫醯氯：<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.15227/orgsyn.049.0018|last1=Paquette|first1=L. A.|last2=Wittenbrook|first2=L. S.|title=2-Chlorothiirane 1,1-Dioxide|journal=Organic Syntheses|volume=49|pp=18|year=1969|url=http://orgsyn.org/Content/pdfs/procedures/CV5P0231.pdf|access-date=2020-08-02|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304121028/http://orgsyn.org/Content/pdfs/procedures/CV5P0231.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

:(CH{{sub|2}}S){{sub|3}} + 9 Cl{{sub|2}} + 6 H{{sub|2}}O → 3 ClCH{{sub|2}}SO{{sub|2}}Cl + 12 HCl

此化合物去質子化及烷基化後可得(SCH<sub>2</sub>)<sub>n</sub>(SCHR)<sub>3-n</sub>。<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1002/recl.19931120611|title=Alkylation of the S-C-S linkage. Towards lipophilic mono- and ditopic heavy-metal receptors containing trithiane building blocks. Molecular structure of cis-2,4,6-tribenzyl-1,3,5-trithiane|year=2010|last1=Edema|first1=Jilles J. H.|last2=Hoogenraad|first2=Marcel|last3=Schoonbeek|first3=Franck S.|last4=Kellogg|first4=Richard M.|last5=Kooijman|first5=Huub|last6=Spek|first6=Anthony L.|journal=Recueil des Travaux Chimiques des Pays-Bas|volume=112|issue=6|pages=370–375}}</ref>

當1,3,5-三硫雜環己烷以甲醛外的[[醛|醛]]或以非對稱[[酮|酮]]製備時，會具有兩種[[同分異構|同分異構]]物：''α''-結構較不穩定，熔點較低，溶解性較高，''β''-結構則相反。<ref name=Ring>{{cite book|title=Multi-Sulfur and Sulfur and Oxygen Five- and Six-Membered Heterocycles, Part 2|volume=21|editor=David S. Breslow, Herman Skolnik|chapter=C3S3 Ring Systems|page=689, 692|isbn=978-0-470-18833-0|year=2009}}</ref>

== 衍生物 ==
除了1,3,5-三硫雜環己烷外，亦有其他同為三硫雜環己烷的[[衍生物|衍生物]]，為其他單價[[官能基|官能基]]替代1,3,5-三硫雜環己烷的氫原子；例如三聚硫代丙酮（2,2,4,4,6,6-六甲基-1,3,5-三硫雜環己烷），為[[硫代丙酮|硫代丙酮]]的三聚物（如圖）。另外亦有[[金剛烷|金剛烷]]相關結構的衍生物。<ref name=Ring/>

